CommentBody: Assigning to TL queue. The case is for Enterprise Auditor

Today we:

Identified that a possible cause of the console locking up was the SP_StaleUsers job being enabled. After disabling that job the Sharepoint group seems to have performed a successful run without issue. 

We then re-enabled the job as a test to run with the entire group at 7 pm tomorrow.

Our next steps are:

You will:

Allow the job to run through the scheduled tasks and attempt to open the console at your earliest convenience. 

If the console hangs during the attempt to access it please provide application logs in the file path below:

Program Files (x86)StealthAuditSADatabaseLogsApplication

As well as a screenshot of any performance impacts from the task manager and the reliability monitor.
Contact did not show for the scheduled meeting today.
